					"type": 23,
					"value": "If you attacked Ketheric on the rooftop of Moonrise Tower, the Myrkulites in the Colony Barracks will be on high alert. If she spots you, she will assume you are one of the traitors that attacked Ketheric - but you can try to convince her otherwise."
